# User Manual

## Overview

This document provides a guide on how to set up and use the auto irrigation system.

## Components

1. Tensiometer
2. Relay module
3. Arduino (or compatible microcontroller)
4. IoT platform for monitoring

## Setup Instructions

1. Connect the tensiometer to the analog pin A0.
2. Connect the relay module to digital pin 7.
3. Upload the firmware to the microcontroller.
4. Run the IoT integration script to monitor system status.

## Usage

The system will automatically turn on the irrigation when the soil moisture level drops below 30%. You can monitor and control the system via the IoT platform.
